		<title>「消尽」原則を迂回するハック</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://text.baldanders.info/remark/2023/11/circumvent-exhaustion/" />
		<id>tag:text.Baldanders.info,2023-11-27:/remark/2023/11/circumvent-exhaustion/</id>
